OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 07 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1946FThe BBC Television service
OL,7,Fresumed, having been off air since 1st
OL,8,FSeptember 1939, due to World War II. At
OL,9,F3pm, one of the original announcers
OL,10,Fwelcomed back viewers:
OL,11,
OL,12,F"Good afternoon everybody. How are you?
OL,13,FDo you remember me, Jasmine Bligh? Well
OL,14,Fhere we are after a lapse of nearly
OL,15,Fseven years ready to start again and of
OL,16,Fcourse we are all terribly excited and
OL,17,Fthrilled."
OL,18,
OL,19,FThe first item on the schedule that day
OL,20,Fwas a repeat showing of the Mickey
OL,21,FMouse cartoon - Mickey's Gala Premier -
OL,22,Fwhich was the final programme to be
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
